President Obama congratulates King Abdullah and the Saudi people on the selection of Prince Salman bin Abd al-Aziz Al Saud as the Crown Prince and Deputy Prime Minister of Saudi Arabia. He praises Prince Salman for his dedication and honor in serving his country as Governor of Riyadh and Minister of Defense. President Obama also highlights Prince Salman's deep faith and commitment to improving the lives of the Saudi people and the security of the region. The United States looks forward to continuing its strong relationship with Crown Prince Salman and deepening the partnership between the two countries.